        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Wherefore I also said,.... Supposing, or on condition of their being guilty of the above things, which was foreseen they would: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I will not drive them out from before you; the seven nations of the Canaanites entirely, and which accounts for the various instances related in the preceding chapter; where it is observed, that they could not, or did not, drive the old inhabitants out of such and such places, because they sinned against the Lord, and he forsook them, and would not assist them in their enterprises, or them to their sloth and indolence: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "but they shall be as thorns in your sides: very troublesome and afflicting, see Numbers 33:55; or for straits, as the Septuagint, or be such as would bring them into tribulation, and distress them, as the Targum; so they often did: ",
        "children": [
          {
